# Misc
# Global gitignore (~/.gitignore_global) ignores __inbox/ whole-dir; re-include the dir
# itself and the specific tracked paths for the zudo-doc-rebuild staging area.
!__inbox/
__inbox/*
!__inbox/new-scaffold/
!__inbox/zcss-preset.json
# …but ignore derived/heavy output inside the tracked scaffold
__inbox/new-scaffold/node_modules
__inbox/new-scaffold/dist
__inbox/new-scaffold/.astro
__inbox/new-scaffold/.output
__inbox/new-scaffold/.wrangler
__inbox/new-scaffold/.playwright-cli
__inbox/new-scaffold/.DS_Store
src/data/
doc/

# Generated skill files (contain machine-specific absolute paths)
.claude/skills/css-wisdom/SKILL.md
.claude/skills/css-wisdom/docs
.claude/skills/css-wisdom/docs-ja
.claude/skills/zcss-wisdom/

# Generated claude-resources docs (auto-generated at build time)
src/content/docs/claude/
src/content/docs/claude-agents/
src/content/docs/claude-md/
src/content/docs/claude-skills/

# Worktrees
worktrees/
